<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>AI Products Website - AI-Pet Translator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="brand">
          <a href="/">Pet Translator</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <header>
      <h1>AI-Pet Translator</h1>
      <p>
        Ever wondered what your furry friends are really thinking? With the
        AI-Pet Translator, wonder no more! This cutting-edge device uses
        advanced artificial intelligence to decode your pet's thoughts and
        feelings, providing real-time translations of barks, meows, and chirps.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether your cat is plotting world domination or your dog just wants a
        belly rub, the AI-Pet Translator promises to bridge the communication
        gap between humans and animals.
      </p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section>
        <h2>Features:</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Emotion Recognition: Analyzes vocal patterns and body language to
            accurately interpret your pet's mood.
          </li>
          <li>
            Behavioral Analysis: Provides insights into your pet's habits,
            preferences, and secret aspirations.
          </li>
          <li>
            Customizable Voice Modulation: Allows you to choose from a range of
            voices to match your pet's personality, from suave and sophisticated
            to goofy and playful.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Pricing:</h2>
        <div>
          <h3>Basic Version - 1000 AI Tokens</h3>
          <p>Unlock the essential features of the AI-Pet Translator.</p>
          <button onclick="buyNow('basic')">Buy Now</button>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Premium Version - 2000 AI Tokens</h3>
          <p>Get access to advanced features and customization options.</p>
          <button onclick="buyNow('premium')">Buy Now</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script>
      // Function to handle buy now button click
      async function buyNow(version) {
        try {
          console.log(version);
          const response = await axios.post("http://localhost:3000/purchase", {
            version,
          });
          // Display the purchase status
          alert(response.data.message);
        } catch (error) {
          console.error("Error:", error);
        }
      }
    </script>
  </body>
